Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.42,0:00:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Haaaaaaaarryyyyy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.66,0:00:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginny, what are you doing here?\NGet out of here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.28,0:00:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there's no place to go.\NThe Death Eaters are all\Nover the castle!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.76,0:00:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I know and they are looking for me.\NAnd if they find me, they're gonna be\Nwith you - you...you...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...you gonna get in trouble.\NGet out of here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.71,0:00:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What you gonna do?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.62,0:00:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't, Ginny! I'm not cut out\Nfor these kind of things.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, you have to do something!\NI don't know what you can do,\Nbut you can do it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:18.48,0:00:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Y..y - you're Harry Potter!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.74,0:00:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,NO!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.18,0:00:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the boy who lived!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.05,0:00:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Ginny! You don't get it!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.14,0:00:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you guys get it! I -
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.52,0:00:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a twelve year old kid!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.37,0:00:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginny, I'm sorry, but... I'm alone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.38,0:00:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's hopeless, alright?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.19,0:00:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been alone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.14,0:00:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrounded by darkness
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.74,0:00:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen how heartless
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.43,0:01:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The world - can be
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.32,0:01:07.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen you cry
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.44,0:01:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You felt like it's hopeless
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.41,0:01:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll always do my best
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.55,0:01:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,To make - you see
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.30,0:01:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That Harry you're not alone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.16,0:01:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're here with me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.19,0:01:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing's ever gonna take us down,\N'cause nothing
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.06,0:01:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can keep me from loving you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.34,0:01:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know it's true
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.38,0:01:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It don't matter what will come to be
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.71,0:01:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love is all we need -\Nto make it through
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.38,0:02:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I know it ain't easy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.08,0:02:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No it ain't easy
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.77,0:02:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But it ain't hard trying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.29,0:02:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So hard trying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.65,0:02:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Every time I see you smiling
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.78,0:02:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And I feel you so close - to me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.44,0:02:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.71,0:02:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That baby you're not alone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:27.45,0:02:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're here with me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.07,0:02:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing is ever gonna bring us down
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.07,0:02:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause nothing can keep me from\Nloving you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.36,0:02:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know it's true
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.35,0:02:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It don't matter what will come to be
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.75,0:02:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love is all we need-\Nto make it through
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm still in trouble
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.65,0:03:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I trip and stumble - try
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.23,0:03:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To make sense of things sometimes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.57,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I look for reasons
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.37,0:03:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't need them
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.43,0:03:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All I need is the look in your eyes
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.58,0:03:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And I realize
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.46,0:03:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Harry
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby you're not alone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.21,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause you're here with me
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And nothing is ever gonna take us down
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.50,0:03:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause - nothing can keep me\Nfrom loving you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.89,0:03:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And you know it's true
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It don't matter what will come to be
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.12,0:03:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love is all we need-\Nto make it through
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.23,0:03:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.54,0:04:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you came back.\NI'm sorry I shouted.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.93,0:04:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It don't matter what will come to be.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.88,0:04:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Our love is all we need
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.59,0:04:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.16,0:04:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,To make...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.41,0:04:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,To make...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.04,0:04:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,To make it...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.13,0:04:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,...through
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.66,0:04:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we've got that four-part\Nharmony out of the way,...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...why don't we look for that horcrux?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.28,0:04:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's true.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.59,0:04:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it could be anywhere.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.01,0:04:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If I had a horcrux, I would drop it\Nin the bottom of the ocean.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.17,0:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I would put it in the pyramid with\Nking Tut and all of his jewels.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.37,0:05:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Or I would blast it into space with a monkey,\Nwho knew nothing about horcruxes.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.40,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Or it could be hidden somewhere around the\Nmundane british countryside.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Our search could [???] months\Nof depressing camping...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.95,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...breaking into Gringotts and drinking\Nboatloads of Polyjiuce potion.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.21,0:05:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, the medallion says: that's dump!\NSo we're not gonna to that.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.27,0:05:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it does say it's in one convenient place.\NGet this: Hogwarts!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.06,0:05:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's awesome. I love Hogwarts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.14,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's even better.\NIt's in Dumbledore's office.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.85,0:05:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, bitching!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.44,0:05:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So let's go! - Oh wait a second!\NWait a second! Hold the phone!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.81,0:05:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you get here? The Death Eaters\Nare all over Hogwarts.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.42,0:05:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I had help.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.16,0:05:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,From whom?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.15,0:05:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's over here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.03,0:05:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Malfoy!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.51,0:05:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, no, no! He's really nice now.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.78,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I - I - I just wanted to say, that song\N#you guys sang was really beautiful.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.51,0:05:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And ah... while - while I was backstage,\NI was...ahm... working on my [singing].
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.54,0:05:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought, ahm... maybe if I could...\Nmaybe I could join you, but you - wrapped\Nit up before I could chime in there.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.12,0:06:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe if you're - do a reprise,\NI could have a little - go at it.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.81,0:06:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And ahm - but as - as Ginny said:\NI'm really nice now...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.82,0:06:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I just feel awful\Nabout what happened.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.42,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I mean: could you argue that\Nthis was my fault?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely - Yes - Oh yes!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.73,0:06:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that would be a save argument,\Nah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.74,0:06:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But - let me ask you one question:
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.98,0:06:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you thing - I'm happy about this?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.58,0:06:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my god, Malfoy! Just because\Nyou're upset doesn't mean you're\Noff the hook.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.39,0:06:35.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, and furthermore: you wanna kick\Nyour own ass, or should we do it for you?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.77,0:06:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...Aaaah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.14,0:06:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess, if you're - giving me the\Noption, I'll - I'll kick my own ass.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.90,0:06:49.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But first, I should teach you how to get\Ninto Dumbledores office. It's ironically\Nthe same way, the Death Eaters got in.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.79,0:06:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, alright.W..w...w why don't you boys\Nhead off to Dumbledores office, okay?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.25,0:06:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginny and I will... will take the invisibility\Ncloak and ah - we will see if we can contact\Nthe order of the phoenix...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...we really haven't seen them\Nthe whole play. So...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.77,0:07:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a good plan. Malfoy, don't touch me!\NLet's get out of here! Let's go!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.32,0:07:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahm...hey! Hey, Hermione! Come here!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Come downstage...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.05,0:07:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...Listen!...Ah... Shit!... Ah... alright,\Nah...hey...aaah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.58,0:07:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So... I've been acting like a\Njerkass lately...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.62,0:07:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,you know that...and, aaah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.18,0:07:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and I'm sorry. It's just: seeing you\Ndance with everyone at the Yule Ball\Njust made me kinda jealous, ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.80,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I was...I was jealous.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.86,0:07:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You were jealous?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.30,0:07:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the third time I say\NI was jealous...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.57,0:07:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...Ro...Ro...Ron, we don't really have\Nto talk about this right now!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.74,0:07:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what if the Death Eaters get us?\NWhat if we don't come back? You know?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.53,0:07:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.21,0:08:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my god...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.22,0:08:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no way...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.02,0:08:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's blueberry.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.41,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I can taste that...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.79,0:08:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta let it settle?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.45,0:08:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.95,0:08:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, spud gum.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.39,0:08:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Take two, take two...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.36,0:08:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You chew it...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.18,0:08:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.68,0:09:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go kill Voldemort!
